    "Transition rules in VFI:\n",
    "- No purchase: $(\\ell, d_{\\rm idx}) \\to (\\ell, \\min(d_{\\rm idx}+1, D_{\\rm MAX}))$\n",
    "- Purchase $j$: $(\\ell, d_{\\rm idx}) \\to (j, 0)$ (paper-$d=1$)"
